  "detailed_description": "Explore the weirdest waterways as you help Marina chart the seas, collect hidden treasures and floating chests, and then use your new found riches to customize your ship!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/39474b3d3daf433bd5a4d0b2f2282e4a.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/39474b3d3daf433bd5a4d0b2f2282e4a.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/39474b3d3daf433bd5a4d0b2f2282e4a.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join the quirky ship captain Marina as she sets sail through a strange ocean!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/38fe64e94280696189ca152a95074881.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/38fe64e94280696189ca152a95074881.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/38fe64e94280696189ca152a95074881.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A charming, hand-animated ship captain: Marina!<br><br>Nothing can sink your ship if you leap over it!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/90ded82d6ea591668d790aa3790651cb.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/90ded82d6ea591668d790aa3790651cb.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/90ded82d6ea591668d790aa3790651cb.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Deftly defy wibblety-wobblety gravity!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/90e3b8b6f5a41e32ba719f451f6714ce.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/90e3b8b6f5a41e32ba719f451f6714ce.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/90e3b8b6f5a41e32ba719f451f6714ce.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sail the wildest waterways ever found as they twist and turn in unpredictable ways.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/2b0e7288838aeca30addaeb347df4544.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/2b0e7288838aeca30addaeb347df4544.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/2b0e7288838aeca30addaeb347df4544.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unique power-ups that will make your head spin.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/e66f2ed5a4a2dfaeab7e228b7dbb4960.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/e66f2ed5a4a2dfaeab7e228b7dbb4960.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/e66f2ed5a4a2dfaeab7e228b7dbb4960.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Multiple modes of play from challenge modes to bizarre features such as turning all projectiles unto ducks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/e10b06afa0bf4ed975d1bff92c7c4ee1.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/e10b06afa0bf4ed975d1bff92c7c4ee1.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/e10b06afa0bf4ed975d1bff92c7c4ee1.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>100 surreal stages that just get stranger-and-stranger.<br><br>10 boss stages that will challenge and bewilder.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/654ea7dc8e9cbb09631016b2e270133f.poster.avif?t=1750748157\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/654ea7dc8e9cbb09631016b2e270133f.webm?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847280/extras/654ea7dc8e9cbb09631016b2e270133f.mp4?t=1750748157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>40 unlockable ship parts to customize your voyage.",
